One walk slowly in and take is sweet time and just do iced coffee. When I inquired, been rudely told that they are served in order. Wonder why the two persons that pay after me got served first. ... right, I wanted warm coffee in Honolulu... when I mention I could have use mobile and received a snarky reply that I would stll have to wait. Well, warm coffee waiting for me for 5 minutes not looking at unsmiling staff. More appealing. Smiled, ran for my coach, mahalo.
